      <title>国库明星作为避风港的赌注，即使特朗普球迷停滞困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/treasuries-star-as-haven-bet-even-as-trump-fans-stagflation-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[震惊的投资者正在担心唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易战争将引发全球衰退，并占据美国国债。至少目前忽略相同的惩罚性关税可能会释放出另一回合通货膨胀的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/treasuries-star-as-haven-bet-even-as-trump-fans-stagflation-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉公牛（Tesla Bull</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/tesla-bull-slashes-stock-price-target-43-citing-musk-and-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街最看涨的特斯拉公司之一的分析师之一将其对该股票的价格目标降低了43％，理由是首席执行官埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）和美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易政策造成的品牌危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/tesla-bull-slashes-stock-price-target-43-citing-musk-and-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 18:44:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Evercore ISI是华尔街最新的公司，可削减S＆amp; P 500目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/evercore-isi-is-latest-firm-on-wall-street-to-cut-s-p-500-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在S＆amp; P 500指数在短短两天内就消除了5.4万亿美元的贸易战争恐惧后，Evercore ISI加入了其他华尔街公司，表示在2025年的目标和Mdash中过于乐观。但是仍然看到股票按年底划分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/evercore-isi-is-latest-firm-on-wall-street-to-cut-s-p-500-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 15:34:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
